{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_03_03",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――新年最初のライブ当日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよ本番だな\nコンディションはどうだ？",
      "startTime": 6.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "凄くいいです\nなんだか、とってもワクワクしてるんです",
      "startTime": 10.94,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。楽しみにしてる\n……呼ばれたな。よし、頑張ってくれ！",
      "startTime": 17.84,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "はい！",
      "startTime": 21.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3566.6666667000018,
          "startTime": 25.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_moon-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "こんにちは、月のテンペストです\nみなさん、明けましておめでとうございます！",
      "startTime": 28.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "みなさんの一年の始まりを、私達の歌で……\nどうか、ほんの少しだけ、彩らせて下さい",
      "startTime": 36.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8000,
          "startTime": 39.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "凄いな、観客がみんな見惚れてる……\nみんな、いつも以上に歌もダンスもキレがいいな",
      "startTime": 46.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "私達の歌、いかがでしたか？",
      "startTime": 50.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "月のテンペストを今年もどうかよろしくお願いします！",
      "startTime": 54.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3245.229021699998,
          "startTime": 57.4452290217
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、凄かったな\n思わず見惚れたよ",
      "startTime": 65.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "良かったです",
      "startTime": 67.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "これも{user}さんのアドバイス通り\nみんなと話し合ったおかげですね",
      "startTime": 72.9433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、ちゃんと話せたんだな\nどんな話をしたんだ？",
      "startTime": 78.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "ライブ直前のレッスンの後、寮で集まって\n一人一人の話を聞いたんです",
      "startTime": 84.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "まず渚は、「月ストはみんな個性があるから\n私なんてどうすればいいか毎日悩んでるよ」……って",
      "startTime": 92.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "すずは、初めは照れてモゴモゴしてたんですけど\n私の歌やダンスのこと「華がある」って褒めてくれて",
      "startTime": 102.2433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "続きを待ってたら「こ、これ以上は無理ですわ！」って\n顔を真っ赤にして……",
      "startTime": 113.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "これ……自分が褒められたことを報告するのって\nよく考えたら凄く恥ずかしいような……",
      "startTime": 120.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "気にしない気にしない\n事務所に戻ったら続きを聞かせてくれ",
      "startTime": 127.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "沙季は、私の歌やダンスを\nはっきりと褒めてくれました",
      "startTime": 134.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "その上で「琴乃ちゃんに嫉妬もしますし、それ以上に\n沢山学べることがあるなって思います」って",
      "startTime": 141.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "こんなにはっきり言えるんだ、ってびっくりしました",
      "startTime": 145.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣も「みんなのこと、凄いなー、羨ましいなーって\n思ってるよ」って言ってました",
      "startTime": 154.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "「お互い羨ましいなって思えるなら\n一緒に頑張れるでしょ。それでいいんじゃない」って",
      "startTime": 160.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "そっか、そういう考え方もあるんだ、って\n少し気が楽になりましたね",
      "startTime": 169.3433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "みんなそれぞれの考え方や悩みがあるんだな……\nなんにせよ、じっくり話し合えたみたいで良かった",
      "startTime": 176.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn020.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。それで、みんな私のことを\n本当に心配してくれてたみたいで",
      "startTime": 185.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn021.m4a",
      "text": "話が終わってもみんなリビングから\n出て行こうとしなくて……",
      "startTime": 191.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn022.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくだから何か観よう、ってことになったんです",
      "startTime": 194.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "待ってくれ、なんだか嫌な予感がする……",
      "startTime": 198.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_03_03-ktn023.m4a",
      "text": "沙季が「千紗から勧められた映画がある」って\nジャケットはパっと見普通だったんですけど……",
      "startTime": 207.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
